                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/3286: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Crane</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-03-02T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 2, 1921—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>82. Your 103, March 1, 1 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department has nothing to add to its number 3, January 5, 5 p.m., and 60,
                    February 8, 7 p.m., by which you should be guided in the matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Colby</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
